{"word":"G4316 - προσαγορεύω - prosagoreúō - pros-ag-or-yoo'-o - Call","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσαγορεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prosagoreúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-ag-or-yoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Call</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஒப்புவி"},{"paragraph":"to speak to, to address, accost, salute"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G58 - ἀγορά - agorá - ag-or-ah'/58\">G58</a> (meaning to <i>harangue</i>); to <i>address</i>, that is, salute by <i>name:</i> - call.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}